+     * {@link EnrollmentCallback} object. It terminates when
+     * {@link EnrollmentCallback#onEnrollmentError(int, CharSequence)} or
+     * {@link EnrollmentCallback#onEnrollmentProgress(int) is called with remaining == 0, at
